### Candidates NOT executed

Candidate 4 (issuedAt: '' placeholder in feedReducer) — FeedCommand type contract
requires issuedAt: string on the payload variants. Removing the placeholder would
require changing the FeedCommand type and adapter signatures, which touches the
domain contract. Deferred to a future sprint with spec change.

Candidate 5 (_channel = untrack(...) lifecycle in FeedList) — the current pattern
is functionally correct and the subscription is cleaned up in onDestroy. Refactoring
the $effect subscription lifecycle would require re-testing Svelte 5 reactivity
edge cases. Low value / higher risk ratio for this sprint.
